{"tid":898287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【技術突破】毋須依賴美俄 日本首次成功自行回收太空艙","createTime":"2018-11-11T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T15:20:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74954674492d771d16391b3499e9590a1a64d30b","tid":898287,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181111/large/1541942807_2a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181111%2Flarge%2F1541942807_2a34.jpg&h=05be8632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本首次成功自行回收太空艙(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n日本宇宙航空研究開發機構（JAXA）周日早上成功回收太空艙，當中運載在國際太空站（ISS）培植的蛋白質結晶體實驗樣本，周二將運送至JAXA於茨城縣的筑波太空中心，用作醫學研究。這是日本首次不依賴美國或俄羅斯，自行從國際太空站回收太空艙。<br />\n日本於9月以H-2B運載火箭成功發射無人補給太空船「白鸛七號」和其他補給品至國際太空站。「白鸛七號」上周四離開國際太空站啟航返回地球，以地平緯度400公里圍繞地球運行，至周日清晨6時24分發射太空艙後，連同國際太空站的太空垃圾進入地球大氣層焚毀。<br />\n84厘米闊、66厘米高的太空艙在降落傘輔助下降落日本東北部南鳥島附近的太平洋海面，JAXA周日稍後派出船隻於小笠原群島附近成功打撈太空艙。JAXA的HTV技術中心總監宮本弘彥指今次回收行動非常成功。<br />\n太空艙運載的實驗樣本，是在國際太空站不受重力影響下培植的高質蛋白質結晶體，可用作探討某些疾病的成因，以及研發用作治療的藥物。<br />\n日本放送協會  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181111/58902005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F58902005&d=oFlJJ1StRo6iSXDaT3IepxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=8b511836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181111%2F58902005&h=5f524edd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181111/58902005</a>"},{"pid":"45ed36cf257837b79fd708a4ca4491090291c016","tid":898287,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"127aba43f1b553cab22eb4991246f3f9ef448d24","tid":898287,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"日本都進步"},{"pid":"72b39574725d0e76b9c98eb6f001f22574caf18b","tid":898287,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c56cd2e6c65834fee852625077f1e46473b246c4","tid":898287,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72b39574725d0e76b9c98eb6f001f22574caf18b","tid":898287,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"無改錯名"}]}